WEBVTT

00:04:28.529 --> 00:04:30.299
Once the new government was in place,

00:04:30.323 --> 00:04:32.470
Hamilton became Secretary of the Treasury,

00:04:32.494 --> 00:04:35.184
and he had a very specific idea in mind.

00:04:35.208 --> 00:04:36.361
And that was

00:04:36.385 --> 00:04:39.356
to do for financial institutions
and infrastructure

00:04:39.380 --> 00:04:42.845
exactly what Madison had done
for constitutions.

00:04:43.665 --> 00:04:45.844
Again, his contemporaries all knew it.

00:04:45.868 --> 00:04:47.702
One of them told Madison,

00:04:47.726 --> 00:04:49.479
who can't have liked it very much,

00:04:49.503 --> 00:04:52.647
that Hamilton was the Newton
of infrastructure.

00:04:53.394 --> 00:04:55.551
The idea was pretty straightforward.

00:04:55.575 --> 00:04:58.276
Hamilton would give
the United States a national bank,

00:04:58.970 --> 00:05:02.376
a permanent national debt --